		<h2>Scouting America's Mission</h2>
  </section>

<p style="font-size: 17px; padding-right: 9cm;">Scouting America's goal is to prepare young people to make ethical and moral choices over <br>their lifetimes by instilling in them <br>the values of the <em>Scout Oath and Law.</em></p>
<ul style="padding-right: 9cm;">
    <li><strong>Character Development</strong></li>
    <li><strong>Leadership Development</strong></li>
