          11045 Parsons Rd, Johns Creek, GA 30097, USA
</a>
<section>
<h2 class="how-to-join">How to Join: Simple and Easy!</h2>
</section>
<ol style="font-size: 17px;padding-right: 9cm;">
    <li><strong>Visit a meeting</strong></li>
    <li><strong>Meet the troop</strong></li>
    <li><strong>Complete a registration form</strong></li>
    <li><strong>Pay dues and get a uniform</strong></li>
</ol>
<section>
<h2 class="involvement">Parent Involvement</h2>
</section>
<p style="font-size: 17px;padding-right: 9cm;">We encourage parent involvement! <br>Whether helping with transportation, organizing campouts,<br> or serving as a merit badge counselor, your support helps the troop thrive!</p>
<section>
<h2 class="faq">FAQ</h2>
</section>
<ul style="font-size: 17px;padding-right: 9cm;">
